+## Suffixes on executables and/or libraries
+
+By default, Siesta uses the default CMake suffixes (if defined):
+
+- SIESTA_SUFFIX (for executables and libraries)
+- SIESTA_EXECUTABLE_SUFFIX
+- SIESTA_SHARED_LIBRARY_SUFFIX
