+For instance, to change the suffixes for the executables:
+```shell
+cmake ... -DSIESTA_EXECUTABLE_SUFFIX=.x
+```
+will create `siesta.x`, and similarly for all other executables.
+
+This can be used to have multiple executables in the same `PATH` using different
+backends, such as a GPU enabled executable `-DSIESTA_EXECUTABLE_SUFFIX=_gpu` etc.
