+# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
+# FDF for interstitial H in a cubic c-Si supercell with 64 atoms
+#
+# E. Artacho, April 1999
+# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
+
+#-------
+## compute-forces F
+SolutionMethod ELSI
+elsi-output-level 3
+elsi-solver elpa
+elsi-elpa-flavor 2
+
+WriteDMHS.NetCDF F
+WriteDM.NetCDF F
+WriteDM T
+
+SystemName          H in 64-atom silicon - ELSI solver
+SystemLabel         sih-elsi
+
+NumberOfAtoms       65
+NumberOfSpecies     2
+
+%block ChemicalSpeciesLabel
+ 1  14  Si
+ 2   1  H 
+%endblock ChemicalSpeciesLabel
+
+PAO.BasisSize       DZP
+PAO.EnergyShift     300 meV
+
+#
+# NOTE: Changed compression factor for H from 0.8 to 0.0 (no compression)
+# to avoid possible bug in 5.0-beta1
+#
+%block PAO.Basis
+  H  1
+  0  1
+  0. 
+  0.0
+%endblock PAO.Basis
+
+LatticeConstant     5.430 Ang
+%block LatticeVectors
+  2.000  0.000  0.000
+  0.000  2.000  0.000
+  0.000  0.000  2.000
+%endblock LatticeVectors
+
+MeshCutoff          100.0 Ry
+
+MaxSCFIterations    20  
+DM.MixingWeight      0.3 
+DM.NumberPulay       4  
+DM.Tolerance         1.d-3
+DM.UseSaveDM             
